{"tid":1879334,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"ive仔 Charles 同 James，你地還清你地條債未？","createTime":"2020-02-14T06:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T10:50:50.000Z","uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"56051131ac5c0b0132bd2e7e7eb8d7ec7e6a4b34","tid":1879334,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港百物騰貴，一個堂食午餐講緊四、五十元，但有餐廳賣麻辣米線，十餸只售十八元！<br />\n這隻「蛤乸」，來自二十六歲的劉子彥（ Charles）。他於 IVE設計系畢業後多次轉工，上年經「雲貴軒」任廚師的舊同學莊沛宏（ James）慫恿，二人向父母借錢，在荃灣沙咀道開設「鹿野麻辣燙專門店」，參考大陸及台灣流行的「自助吧」形式，攤出所有食物給客人秤，並以重量來計算價錢。<br />\n由於不設最低消費，蔬菜及肉類劃一價錢，麵底只售七元，食物成本襟計。加上門面太高級、按量收費太新穎&hellip;&hellip;四個蝕錢位令首月虧損三萬。兩位創業新手處處碰壁，他們慨嘆：「再咁落去，唔使半年就頂唔住！」"},{"pid":"973ba7dd99e59ee97afa8340b8f6a887ca25cd8c","tid":1879334,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:03:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://funnyday0.blogspot.com/2015/09/19.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffunnyday0.blogspot.com%2F2015%2F09%2F19.html%3Fm%3D1&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKRzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=d5c7c7b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://funnyday0.blogspot.com/2015/09/19.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49f5e79f6e70b090e4d04de2cf11fe0ac44dcff","tid":1879334,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:05:19.000Z","msg":"威威做老板幾個月<br />\n<br />\n條債要成家還成世🙈"},{"pid":"231ab02606932fc2d089ba63387af6ed813a4575","tid":1879334,"uid":294013,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:05:30.000Z","msg":"咁屈蛇你張樓契呢?"},{"pid":"a9573e71c5c4a7d7324e519ad6a73ec173c0f099","tid":1879334,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:06:15.000Z","msg":"返工都返唔掂學人做生意🙈<br />\n<b